50 years, Gordon.

1:42:39.325 --> 1:42:40.702
I didn't know you had it in you.

1:42:44.956 --> 1:42:49.294
I was just trying to protect
everyone in here.

1:42:49.336 --> 1:42:52.839
And I'm just trying to protect
everyone out there.

